name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.block.access.key.update.interval
description: Interval in minutes at which namenode updates its access keys.

name: dfs.ha.fencing.ssh.connect-timeout
description:
SSH connection timeout, in milliseconds, to use with the builtin
    sshfence fencer.

name: mapreduce.task.timeout
description:
The number of milliseconds before a task will be
  terminated if it neither reads an input, writes an output, nor
  updates its status string.  A value of 0 disables the timeout.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.pathcache.concurrency-level
description:
Uses the concurrency level to create a fixed number of hashtable
    segments, each governed by its own write lock.

name: dfs.namenode.checkpoint.check.period
description:
The SecondaryNameNode and CheckpointNode will poll the NameNode
  every 'dfs.namenode.checkpoint.check.period' seconds to query the number
  of uncheckpointed transactions. Support multiple time unit suffix(case insensitive),
  as described in dfs.heartbeat.interval.If no time unit is specified then
  seconds is assumed.

name: fs.s3a.list.version
description:
Select which version of the S3 SDK's List Objects API to use.  Currently
    support 2 (default) and 1 (older API).

name: dfs.webhdfs.netty.high.watermark
description: High watermark configuration to Netty for Datanode WebHdfs.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.move.thread-count
description: The number of threads used to move files.
